erary giant.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aFictionxHistory and criticism. 0aFictionxTechnique. 0aRealism in literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aRojas, Carlos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRojas, Carlos.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDuke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076691240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478022916?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478022916423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478022916/original  a978-3-11-076691-2  Duke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles